EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   08 THRU 10 JUL WITHIN 25 MILES OF
   57-28.5N 008-14.1W. VESSELS INTENDING TO
   ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL
   ON VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1659/15(36,37,51),
   VESSEL LOCATED SAFE.
3. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1652/15.
4. CANCEL THIS MSG 101900Z JUL 15.
